/-!
# Tight Bound Witness: R+D+H at N=10

A concrete 10-element algebra satisfying all three capabilities simultaneously:
  R (self-simulating): retraction pair Q(2)/E(3) with E-transparency
  D (self-describing): classifier τ(4) with Kripke dichotomy
  H (self-hosting): Branch(ρ=7), Compose(η=8), Inert(g=6), Y(9) fixed-point

**Tight bound theorem**: The three capability axioms with 10 distinguished
